{"tid":1632332,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[ 突 發 ] 跟住做香港人一定會贏","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:37:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T17:54:01.000Z","uid":142010,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"72b708d8f8f7749823eee67163248b779431ad1c","tid":1632332,"uid":142010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:37:48.000Z","msg":"Sorry 呃左你哋入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我覺得 而家成個觀感 都偏向負面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想提醒大家 如果要開post 建議都係攞返啲正面啲嘅標題<br />\n明明我係twitter睇都冇事嘅！<br />\n<br />\n今日雖然不完美 但我地仲有時間改善<br />\n一定唔好俾人分化到！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不割蓆 不分化 不譴責</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n香港人 加油 反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20e4103ccd668aef11b3552e14a434922ae900fa","tid":1632332,"uid":142010,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:38:57.000Z","msg":"對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修<br />\n<br />\n1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX<br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.MEMO紙<br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.善用1823<br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.蟲系魔法師<br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):<br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚<br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢飛個靚髮或者化下妝就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命<br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"99fa33aaa3c93041366726272412d10b74dde51c","tid":1632332,"uid":110332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:38:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文宣緊急法，勇武養精蓄銳，永遠不會割不屌，只會補鑊！</span><br />\n<br />\n香港轉咗入大直路啦，唔係依家先黎炒嘛？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632214\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632214</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d66df74d1c705d3ed5e1a10959b95252e73161e0","tid":1632332,"uid":312193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:39:01.000Z","msg":"內容正確<br />\n可惜係標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b838c9712dc3edf9533cd4e431166a96ee0ba2d","tid":1632332,"uid":142010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:39:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8819794b64ee9ffec2c13540f3bdaa12b382f3da","tid":1632332,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:39:29.000Z","msg":"團結！"},{"pid":"9d836dd82b1ea3a5a398d195c68fe59abad77ccb","tid":1632332,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:40:10.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山<br />\n<br />\n唔好被分化<br />\n<br />\n做自己覺得係啱嘅野"},{"pid":"4aea86dbbce9ec69bf7969390198eb58d85f67e4","tid":1632332,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:52:29.000Z","msg":"推俾外國旅客 咪俾黨鐵賺錢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632118\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632118</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"adb38065748160eb89df9a58b4962af400809af0","tid":1632332,"uid":259319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:52:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[18區開花]